### プリセット DQL マッピング
- recent(N): `LIST SORT file.mtime DESC LIMIT {N}`
- tag(X): `LIST FROM #{X}`
- journal(N): `LIST FROM "journals" SORT file.name DESC LIMIT {N}`
- todo: `LIST WHERE file.open_tasks SORT file.mtime DESC`

